{
  "texts": [
    "For the arXiv dataset, the optimal ratio is 50%.",
    "In addition, SciBERT achieved the best Macro_F 1 across all compositions and average scores on both datasets, with a notable advantage on the arXiv dataset.",
    "It's important to note that the average chapter length in the arXiv dataset exceeds 790 words, surpassing SciBERT's 512-token input limit.",
    "Similarly, sections like Results and Conclusions in the PubMed dataset also exceed this limit.",
    "Therefore, filtering out important information, such as the beginning and end of chapters, is beneficial for reducing input length while enhancing the performance of the SFR task."
  ]
}